<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19932</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空和他的同伴都被绑在了道观的一间房里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19933</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我早上再来收拾你们。”镇元大仙说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他转身离开了房间。唐僧哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这一路上各种危险就已经够了。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我自己的徒弟还给我惹麻烦！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“冷静，师父。”悟空说，“我们会出去的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51074</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父，这都是悟空的错。”八戒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他偷的人参果，他弄倒的树。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64700</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“偷人参果可是你的主意！”悟空大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我饿的时候就忍不住。”八戒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你应该拒绝去偷人参果啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们别吵了，想想怎么逃出去吧。”悟净说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80330</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有个主意，”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我们必须等到镇元大仙睡着了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天夜里悟空念了个咒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97674</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他缩成了一个豌豆大小，然后从捆他的绳子里溜了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97675</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他迅速地给他的伙伴们松绑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们走！”他低声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一行人悄悄地离开了黑暗又安静的道观。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117599</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们走到外面的时候，太阳刚好升起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这很简单啊！”他们沿着路走的时候八戒说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望你们都从这件事里吸取教训。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然一个很大的声音说道：“你们不可能从我这里逃出去的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>镇元大仙朝着他们飞过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空抽出了金箍棒挥打起来。镇元大仙躲开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155105</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒用他的钉耙去攻击，悟净也用他的宝杖去刺镇元大仙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>镇元大仙的动作非常快。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挥舞着手臂，他的袖子朝着悟空一行人扫下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们又一次被扫进了袖子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在道观后院，镇元大仙让他的道士们点起火来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给我拿个大的油锅。”镇元大仙说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要把这些小偷炸了。我们就从孙悟空开始吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>道士们把一个巨大无比的油锅抬到了房间里，放在了火上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊哦！”悟空想，“我在那油锅里坐一天都不会受伤，但唐僧是凡人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他会被烧死的！”。他看到了附近的一个狮子雕像。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空快速念了个咒，那个雕像变成自己，然后他就消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把孙悟空扔进油锅里！”镇元大仙说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个道士把那雕像当做了悟空，要把它抬起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这猴子比看上去的重得多。”一个道士喘着粗气说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！”另一个道士也气喘吁吁地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最终他们把雕像拉到了油锅旁扔了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>啪！ 油锅裂成了两半。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那猴子骗了我们！”镇元大仙叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他把这雕像变成了他的模样！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那只坏猴子！”八戒大叫，“他不带我们就逃了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你认为他真的离开了吗？”唐僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看看四周啊！”八戒说，“他走了！他可能回花果山去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我敢保证，他现在一定在花园里玩儿的开心呢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们呢，却被困在这里！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得他是不会离开我们的。”悟净说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧哭了起来。镇元大仙气得发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309559</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314648</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孙悟空想要逃走就已经很坏了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他一定要砸坏我的油锅吗？”他跺着脚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再拿一口油锅来。我们把他的同伴们炸了，就从唐僧开始！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>